{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01YEA3CckYwoTFBFTB4B2qz6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01LBFbPQL65SeASCARmijo1T","name":"Agent","input":{"subagent_type":"debug","prompt":"Fix the remaining issues found in the Round 2 codex review for task B-config-switching. The review file is at .trellis/tasks/04-22-B-config-switching/codex-review-20260423-1212.txt. There are 3 Major and 2 Minor issues to fix:\n\n**1. [Major] Pre-warm spawn hash race**\n- File: src/components/chat/ChatPanel.tsx:843-847\n- Problem: `spawnConfigHash()` is computed AFTER `await spawnSession()` in the pre-warm path, the same pattern that was already fixed in InputBar.tsx. \n- Fix: Apply the same fix as InputBar — compute spawnConfigHash() BEFORE await spawnSession(), store as preSpawnConfigHash, use pre-computed value when writing sessionMeta.\n\n**2. [Major] Auto-retry spawn hash race**\n- File: src/hooks/useStreamProcessor.ts:1713-1717\n- Problem: Same post-await hash computation pattern in the auto-retry spawn path.\n- Fix: Same approach — compute hash before await, use pre-computed value after.\n\n**3. [Major] Spawn failure loses file attachments**\n- File: src/components/chat/InputBar.tsx:811 (clearFiles before spawn), catch block at line 1107 (only restores text), early returns at lines 851 and 864.\n- Problem: clearFiles() runs before spawn attempt. If spawn fails, catch block restores rawInput but not file attachments. Also early validation returns at 851/864 lose files.\n- Fix: Save file attachments before clearing, restore them in the catch block. For early returns, restore files similarly to how rawInput is restored.\n\n**4. [Minor] GeneralTab labels not disambiguated**\n- File: src/components/settings/GeneralTab.tsx (or wherever the settings model selector is)\n- Problem: Settings page still shows identical provider model names for all opus variants, while ModelSelector was already fixed.\n- Fix: Apply same disambiguation pattern as ModelSelector — show \"provider-model (Opus 4.7)\" etc.\n\n**5. [Minor] clearPrefix before interaction card check**\n- File: src/components/chat/InputBar.tsx\n- Problem: Prefix visual chip is lost on the blocking return path even though text content is preserved.\n- Fix: Move clearPrefix() after the interaction card check, or restore prefix on the blocking return path.","model":"opus","run_in_background":true,"name":"debug-round2","description":"Debug fix review round 2 issues"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":160,"cache_read_input_tokens":86273,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":160},"output_tokens":13,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7dcb2e38-d9a0-456f-a0b4-50bcd29e86c0","uuid":"a811db96-f60d-4538-a9a4-60e4174ae1b7"}
{"type":"system","subtype":"task_started","task_id":"ad502f9bcf549f3c7","tool_use_id":"toolu_01LBFbPQL65SeASCARmijo1T","description":"Debug fix review round 2 issues","task_type":"local_agent","prompt":"Fix the remaining issues found in the Round 2 codex review for task B-config-switching. The review file is at .trellis/tasks/04-22-B-config-switching/codex-review-20260423-1212.txt. There are 3 Major and 2 Minor issues to fix:\n\n**1. [Major] Pre-warm spawn hash race**\n- File: src/components/chat/ChatPanel.tsx:843-847\n- Problem: `spawnConfigHash()` is computed AFTER `await spawnSession()` in the pre-warm path, the same pattern that was already fixed in InputBar.tsx. \n- Fix: Apply the same fix as InputBar — compute spawnConfigHash() BEFORE await spawnSession(), store as preSpawnConfigHash, use pre-computed value when writing sessionMeta.\n\n**2. [Major] Auto-retry spawn hash race**\n- File: src/hooks/useStreamProcessor.ts:1713-1717\n- Problem: Same post-await hash computation pattern in the auto-retry spawn path.\n- Fix: Same approach — compute hash before await, use pre-computed value after.\n\n**3. [Major] Spawn failure loses file attachments**\n- File: src/components/chat/InputBar.tsx:811 (clearFiles before spawn), catch block at line 1107 (only restores text), early returns at lines 851 and 864.\n- Problem: clearFiles() runs before spawn attempt. If spawn fails, catch block restores rawInput but not file attachments. Also early validation returns at 851/864 lose files.\n- Fix: Save file attachments before clearing, restore them in the catch block. For early returns, restore files similarly to how rawInput is restored.\n\n**4. [Minor] GeneralTab labels not disambiguated**\n- File: src/components/settings/GeneralTab.tsx (or wherever the settings model selector is)\n- Problem: Settings page still shows identical provider model names for all opus variants, while ModelSelector was already fixed.\n- Fix: Apply same disambiguation pattern as ModelSelector — show \"provider-model (Opus 4.7)\" etc.\n\n**5. [Minor] clearPrefix before interaction card check**\n- File: src/components/chat/InputBar.tsx\n- Problem: Prefix visual chip is lost on the blocking return path even though text content is preserved.\n- Fix: Move clearPrefix() after the interaction card check, or restore prefix on the blocking return path.","uuid":"c672ab71-1469-4d74-a941-74eee3561d42","session_id":"7dcb2e38-d9a0-456f-a0b4-50bcd29e86c0"}
